WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 4=

00:01:37.850 --> 00:01:39.730 line:80%
While searching for clues,

00:01:39.980 --> 00:01:41.090 line:80%
I unexpectedly learned

00:01:41.340 --> 00:01:43.780 line:80%
the Changs had an old steward
surnamed Jiang.

00:01:44.930 --> 00:01:45.850 line:80%
Five years ago,

00:01:46.180 --> 00:01:48.340 line:80%
the steward retired to his hometown

00:01:48.570 --> 00:01:50.090 line:80%
and took a boy with him.

00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:51.370 line:80%
After much investigation,

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:53.850 line:80%
at Steward Jiang's grave,

00:01:53.930 --> 00:01:56.700 line:80%
I found Mr. Jiang,
who resembles the late Mr. Chang,

00:01:57.180 --> 00:01:58.420 line:80%
or rather,

00:01:58.980 --> 00:02:00.490 line:80%
the real Chang Ning.

00:02:03.900 --> 00:02:04.740 line:80%
If he's Chang Ning,

00:02:05.090 --> 00:02:05.930 line:80%
who am I?

00:02:06.460 --> 00:02:07.686 line:80%
I also want to know who you are

00:02:08.093 --> 00:02:09.210 line:80%
and why you impersonated me.

00:02:11.690 --> 00:02:13.180 line:80%
My mother died 12 years ago.

00:02:13.620 --> 00:02:14.706 line:80%
You claim to be Chang Ning,

00:02:15.020 --> 00:02:16.740 line:80%
but do you know Mrs. Chang's birthday?

00:02:16.843 --> 00:02:18.063 line:80%
The 16th day of the 11th month.

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:19.180 line:80%
Where was Mrs. Chang from?

00:02:19.190 --> 00:02:20.050 line:80%
Suzhou.

00:02:20.060 --> 00:02:20.960 line:80%
What was her favorite?

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:21.810 line:80%
She liked sweets.

00:02:22.370 --> 00:02:23.460 line:80%
Her favorite was

00:02:23.690 --> 00:02:25.140 line:80%
Furong Pastry

00:02:25.650 --> 00:02:26.860 line:80%
from Jiangnan Yipinju.

00:02:32.930 --> 00:02:34.650 line:80%
Under the desk in the study,

00:02:34.661 --> 00:02:35.881 line:80%
there is a character engraved.

00:02:37.210 --> 00:02:38.300 line:80%
What is it?

00:02:43.650 --> 00:02:44.650 line:80%
16 years ago,

00:02:45.090 --> 00:02:46.356 line:80%
my father went to the demon sect

00:02:46.580 --> 00:02:48.020 line:80%
to help Ms. Cai Pingshu.

00:02:48.530 --> 00:02:49.583 line:80%
My mother suddenly fell ill

00:02:49.650 --> 00:02:51.263 line:80%
and accidentally tipped over the stove,

00:02:51.650 --> 00:02:52.900 line:80%
burning my left arm.

00:02:53.210 --> 00:02:54.050 line:80%
Do you have

00:02:54.210 --> 00:02:55.050 line:80%
a scar on your arm?

00:03:06.370 --> 00:03:07.210 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:03:07.490 --> 00:03:08.780 line:80%
Too afraid to show it?

00:03:09.530 --> 00:03:11.580 line:80%
Clearly, he's hiding something.

00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:13.300 line:80%
I suppose everyone knows

00:03:13.300 --> 00:03:15.370 line:80%
who the real one is now.

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:21.740 line:80%
The Chang residence has been dug up.

00:03:22.740 --> 00:03:23.766 line:80%
Everything was destroyed.

00:03:24.410 --> 00:03:26.370 line:80%
Those with ulterior motives

00:03:26.490 --> 00:03:27.876 line:80%
can surely make up stories at will.

00:03:28.860 --> 00:03:29.700 line:80%
Let me ask you.

00:03:30.300 --> 00:03:31.300 line:80%
On the 3rd shelf, 4th row

00:03:31.580 --> 00:03:33.530 line:80%
of my father's study bookshelf,

00:03:33.713 --> 00:03:34.713 line:80%
there's also a character.

00:03:35.530 --> 00:03:36.580 line:80%
What is it?

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:41.090 line:80%
A dog once bit me when I was little,

00:03:41.580 --> 00:03:42.600 line:80%
leaving a scar on my calf.

00:03:43.530 --> 00:03:44.930 line:80%
Do you dare roll up your pants

00:03:45.410 --> 00:03:46.250 line:80%
so everyone can see?

00:03:46.780 --> 00:03:47.620 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:03:48.060 --> 00:03:49.180 line:80%
There is no scar.

00:03:49.490 --> 00:03:50.330 line:80%
Indeed.

00:03:50.740 --> 00:03:53.370 line:80%
It's your story against mine.

00:03:53.970 --> 00:03:56.460 line:80%
All of you here are respected figures.

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:58.650 line:80%
Yet you've fallen
into this trap of self-proof.

00:04:00.020 --> 00:04:01.020 line:80%
If so,

00:04:01.180 --> 00:04:02.140 line:80%
why not fight

00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:04.900 line:80%
with your family's Willow Sword?

00:04:05.180 --> 00:04:06.020 line:80%
This swordsmanship

00:04:06.340 --> 00:04:07.410 line:80%
can't be faked, right?

00:04:10.370 --> 00:04:11.340 line:80%
As you wish.

00:04:11.810 --> 00:04:12.650 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:04:12.860 --> 00:04:13.810 line:80%
you knew my father well.

00:04:13.980 --> 00:04:15.680 line:80%
You know I've been sickly
since childhood,

00:04:15.900 --> 00:04:17.410 line:80%
only practicing internal cultivation

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:18.363 line:80%
to strengthen meridians,

00:04:18.396 --> 00:04:19.696 line:80%
unable to train in swordsmanship.

00:04:19.820 --> 00:04:20.660 line:80%
That's why my father

00:04:20.900 --> 00:04:22.140 line:80%
kept me away from Jianghu,

00:04:22.410 --> 00:04:23.376 line:80%
never letting me go out.

00:04:24.170 --> 00:04:25.010 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:04:25.500 --> 00:04:26.700 line:80%
if you intend to play a trick,

00:04:27.020 --> 00:04:28.170 line:80%
at least take it seriously

00:04:28.410 --> 00:04:30.410 line:80%
and pick someone
skilled in martial arts.

00:04:30.610 --> 00:04:31.580 line:80%
This way,

00:04:32.170 --> 00:04:33.476 line:80%
you're only humiliating yourself.

00:04:33.780 --> 00:04:34.620 line:80%
You...

00:04:35.140 --> 00:04:36.090 line:80%
As everyone knows,

00:04:36.090 --> 00:04:37.940 line:80%
Ning has been sickly since childhood.

00:04:38.210 --> 00:04:39.820 line:80%
It is understandable that Mr. Chang

00:04:39.820 --> 00:04:41.140 line:80%
did not teach him martial arts.

00:04:42.970 --> 00:04:43.810 line:80%
Xiuming,

00:04:44.170 --> 00:04:45.580 line:80%
you know Chang Haosheng well,

00:04:45.730 --> 00:04:47.290 line:80%
and you treated his injuries.

00:04:47.530 --> 00:04:48.410 line:80%
Speak up.

00:04:48.700 --> 00:04:49.540 line:80%
Who is real?

00:04:49.780 --> 00:04:50.620 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:51.780 line:80%
you found the person.

00:04:52.700 --> 00:04:53.970 line:80%
I only treat injuries.

00:04:54.730 --> 00:04:56.650 line:80%
I don't care who he is.

00:04:57.090 --> 00:04:58.850 line:80%
- You...
- My father just passed.

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:00.290 line:80%
Instead of seeking the culprit,

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:02.050 line:80%
you found a man

00:05:02.050 --> 00:05:03.170 line:80%
resembling my father

00:05:03.780 --> 00:05:05.850 line:80%
and put on such a show.

00:05:06.530 --> 00:05:07.900 line:80%
What do you want?

00:05:08.170 --> 00:05:09.610 line:80%
Who'd act with you?

00:05:09.650 --> 00:05:10.490 line:80%
Enough.

00:05:11.970 --> 00:05:13.020 line:80%
This is serious.

00:05:13.410 --> 00:05:14.650 line:80%
Since it's hard to tell,

00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:16.290 line:80%
let me test

00:05:16.610 --> 00:05:18.650 line:80%
their internal cultivation.

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:21.180 line:80%
Uncle Li,

00:05:21.626 --> 00:05:22.540 line:80%
that requires injecting

00:05:22.540 --> 00:05:23.850 line:80%
internal energy into meridians.

00:05:24.410 --> 00:05:25.340 line:80%
Isn't that too harsh?

00:05:26.900 --> 00:05:27.740 line:80%
Yunke?

00:05:30.020 --> 00:05:31.140 line:80%
Zhao is right.

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:34.530 line:80%
Don't harm the real Ning.

00:05:56.970 --> 00:05:57.810 line:80%
Uncle Li,

00:05:57.821 --> 00:05:59.300 line:80%
Chang Ning's injuries are not healed.

00:05:59.311 --> 00:06:00.650 line:80%
At this rate, he may die.

00:06:01.650 --> 00:06:03.020 line:80%
Their true energy

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:05.340 line:80%
was cultivated
with the Changs' techniques.

00:06:12.410 --> 00:06:13.610 line:80%
Their meridians are damaged.

00:06:13.730 --> 00:06:14.683 line:80%
Their lives are at risk.

00:06:15.290 --> 00:06:16.130 line:80%
Yunke,

00:06:16.380 --> 00:06:18.140 line:80%
let me take them back to heal.

00:06:18.500 --> 00:06:19.406 line:80%
Examine them tomorrow.

00:06:37.780 --> 00:06:38.620 line:80%
He's fine.

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:40.180 line:80%
He'll wake up soon.

00:06:41.580 --> 00:06:42.460 line:80%
You don't care

00:06:42.820 --> 00:06:44.140 line:80%
who the real one is?

00:06:44.610 --> 00:06:45.500 line:80%
As I said,

00:06:46.020 --> 00:06:47.050 line:80%
I only treat illnesses.

00:06:52.580 --> 00:06:54.700 line:80%
That's Breeze, my father's favorite.

00:06:56.900 --> 00:06:58.580 line:80%
Drinks in spring

00:06:59.940 --> 00:07:03.380 line:80%
last ten years.

00:07:07.410 --> 00:07:08.290 line:80%
Since you know

00:07:08.290 --> 00:07:09.650 line:80%
so many family secrets,

00:07:10.460 --> 00:07:12.090 line:80%
you must be close to Chang.

00:07:14.340 --> 00:07:15.180 line:80%
Tomorrow,

00:07:16.090 --> 00:07:17.210 line:80%
if there's more to say,

00:07:17.780 --> 00:07:18.730 line:80%
think it through first,

00:07:19.610 --> 00:07:20.580 line:80%
or you two

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:22.090 line:80%
may not end well.

00:07:43.530 --> 00:07:44.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:45.850 line:80%
why hold an empty bowl?

00:07:46.290 --> 00:07:47.170 line:80%
Craving meat?

00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:51.580 line:80%
I want wonton.

00:07:51.940 --> 00:07:52.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:53.340 --> 00:07:54.340 line:80%
does the collarbone hurt

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:56.290 line:80%
when pierced?

00:07:56.820 --> 00:07:57.660 line:80%
Of course,

00:07:58.210 --> 00:07:59.140 line:80%
why ask that?

00:08:00.090 --> 00:08:01.730 line:80%
I just went to the kitchen for food.

00:08:02.290 --> 00:08:03.610 line:80%
Zhuang Shu said

00:08:04.210 --> 00:08:05.050 line:80%
that tomorrow,

00:08:05.140 --> 00:08:06.410 line:80%
if no conclusion is reached,

00:08:06.700 --> 00:08:07.540 line:80%
Uncle Li

00:08:07.730 --> 00:08:09.820 line:80%
will lock their collarbones,

00:08:10.057 --> 00:08:11.256 line:80%
crippling their martial arts,

00:08:11.380 --> 00:08:12.413 line:80%
to prevent future trouble.

00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:38.410 line:80%
Zhuo...

00:08:39.780 --> 00:08:40.620 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:08:46.100 --> 00:08:46.940 line:80%
Sleeping drug.

00:09:19.500 --> 00:09:20.340 line:80%
Chang Ning!

00:09:32.860 --> 00:09:33.700 line:80%
Bring the crossbow.

00:09:59.570 --> 00:10:01.140 line:80%
Why pull me down?

00:10:03.100 --> 00:10:04.290 line:80%
Didn't you come here

00:10:04.620 --> 00:10:06.020 line:80%
to leave with me?

00:10:06.380 --> 00:10:07.220 line:80%
Your leaving

00:10:07.570 --> 00:10:08.900 line:80%
will only prove you're a spy.

00:10:09.650 --> 00:10:10.490 line:80%
When you're wanted,

00:10:10.530 --> 00:10:11.530 line:80%
how will you survive?

00:10:11.900 --> 00:10:13.220 line:80%
I'm already doomed.

00:10:14.101 --> 00:10:15.278 line:80%
If I can't avenge while alive,

00:10:15.289 --> 00:10:16.129 line:80%
death is better.

00:10:16.330 --> 00:10:17.180 line:80%
Don't you know

00:10:17.180 --> 00:10:18.220 line:80%
what they will do to me?

00:10:19.740 --> 00:10:20.580 line:80%
Capture the assassin!

00:10:23.570 --> 00:10:24.740 line:80%
We are not assassins.

00:10:25.900 --> 00:10:27.810 line:80%
You must be from Taichu Temple.

00:10:28.330 --> 00:10:30.100 line:80%
We are from Qingque Sect.

00:10:35.060 --> 00:10:38.660 line:80%
(Qiu Yuanfeng, Lord of Taichu Temple)

00:10:38.780 --> 00:10:40.380 line:80%
You must be here

00:10:40.740 --> 00:10:42.410 line:80%
to attend the memorial, right?

00:10:42.933 --> 00:10:44.369 line:80%
(Wang Yuanjing)
Such a long journey

00:10:44.380 --> 00:10:45.220 line:80%
must be exhausting.

00:10:45.330 --> 00:10:47.140 line:80%
Did you really get here by accident?

00:10:48.740 --> 00:10:49.580 line:80%
Yes.

00:10:50.740 --> 00:10:51.810 line:80%
A misunderstanding.

00:10:53.020 --> 00:10:53.860 line:80%
Originally...

00:11:00.290 --> 00:11:01.130 line:80%
Chang Ning!

00:11:04.930 --> 00:11:05.770 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:11:07.780 --> 00:11:08.620 line:80%
Lord Qiu,

00:11:08.930 --> 00:11:10.530 line:80%
he's a fugitive from Qingque Sect.

00:11:11.060 --> 00:11:12.160 line:80%
Please let me take him away.

00:11:13.450 --> 00:11:14.290 line:80%
Who are you?

00:11:14.570 --> 00:11:16.020 line:80%
Why did you attack me?

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:18.780 line:80%
You're the one who raided Chang Fort

00:11:19.450 --> 00:11:21.100 line:80%
and killed my father.

00:11:25.810 --> 00:11:27.140 line:80%
An impostor's words

00:11:27.220 --> 00:11:28.170 line:80%
are not credible.

00:11:31.570 --> 00:11:33.020 line:80%
I'm the killer?

00:11:34.100 --> 00:11:34.940 line:80%
Where's the evidence?

00:11:35.220 --> 00:11:37.100 line:80%
When my father escorted me out,

00:11:38.020 --> 00:11:40.100 line:80%
he fought one of the assassins
for a long time.

00:11:46.220 --> 00:11:48.290 line:80%
His attacks had a sandalwood fragrance,

00:11:49.020 --> 00:11:49.930 line:80%
the same

00:11:50.140 --> 00:11:51.780 line:80%
as Lord Qiu carries.

00:11:53.100 --> 00:11:54.170 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:11:54.690 --> 00:11:56.330 line:80%
Taichu Temple is so close to Chang Fort.

00:11:57.050 --> 00:11:58.810 line:80%
Yet they knew nothing

00:11:59.020 --> 00:11:59.940 line:80%
of the great commotion

00:12:00.020 --> 00:12:01.290 line:80%
in Chang Fort?

00:12:02.740 --> 00:12:03.580 line:80%
Indeed.

00:12:06.290 --> 00:12:07.780 line:80%
I wasn't at the temple back then.

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:09.330 line:80%
Moreover,

00:12:09.330 --> 00:12:10.810 line:80%
Chang Fort had been hidden

00:12:11.170 --> 00:12:12.563 line:80%
in the mountains for over a decade,

00:12:12.930 --> 00:12:14.650 line:80%
cut off from the outside world.

00:12:14.930 --> 00:12:16.330 line:80%
As for the fragrance,

00:12:16.980 --> 00:12:17.820 line:80%
Yuanjing,

00:12:18.140 --> 00:12:19.860 line:80%
please explain to everyone.

00:12:24.620 --> 00:12:25.460 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:12:25.650 --> 00:12:27.650 line:80%
this incense is our special Ethereal,

00:12:28.020 --> 00:12:30.410 line:80%
crafted with rosewood and Qiong flowers.

00:12:30.620 --> 00:12:31.530 line:80%
It calms energy

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:32.370 line:80%
and aids cultivation.

00:12:32.430 --> 00:12:33.290 line:80%
Many practitioners

00:12:33.290 --> 00:12:34.130 line:80%
sought it.

00:12:34.650 --> 00:12:37.020 line:80%
Mr. Chang's suspicion of Yuanfeng

00:12:37.140 --> 00:12:38.620 line:80%
was just youthful ignorance.

00:12:38.740 --> 00:12:39.810 line:80%
What Mr. Chang?

00:12:40.220 --> 00:12:41.410 line:80%
He is clearly an unknown spy,

00:12:41.410 --> 00:12:42.810 line:80%
stirring discord.

00:12:43.500 --> 00:12:45.020 line:80%
Lord Qiu, you appear clean.

00:12:45.570 --> 00:12:46.636 line:80%
You only got your position

00:12:46.980 --> 00:12:49.620 line:80%
after Mr. Wu Yuanying's death,

00:12:49.780 --> 00:12:52.860 line:80%
yet you expelled
his beloved Luo Yuanrong...

00:12:52.860 --> 00:12:53.700 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:12:53.810 --> 00:12:54.756 line:80%
How dare you smear me?

00:12:56.450 --> 00:12:58.170 line:80%
Such a schemer

00:12:58.810 --> 00:13:00.140 line:80%
should be executed.

00:13:00.740 --> 00:13:01.580 line:80%
Wait.

00:13:12.500 --> 00:13:14.010 line:80%
Pingchun, Xiaofeng,

00:13:14.170 --> 00:13:15.010 line:80%
you're back.

00:13:15.186 --> 00:13:16.485 line:80%
When we were about to come back,

00:13:16.530 --> 00:13:17.923 line:80%
we met Mr. Jiang at the cliff base.

00:13:18.690 --> 00:13:19.690 line:80%
Mr. Jiang said

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:21.410 line:80%
Ning is in trouble

00:13:21.740 --> 00:13:22.846 line:80%
and asked us to take him up.

00:13:22.980 --> 00:13:23.830 line:80%
Mr. Jiang,

00:13:23.860 --> 00:13:24.980 line:80%
Lord Qi is also here.

00:13:25.290 --> 00:13:26.130 line:80%
Tell us

00:13:26.500 --> 00:13:27.900 line:80%
everything you know.

00:13:28.530 --> 00:13:29.569 line:80%
He is the real Chang Ning.

00:13:37.690 --> 00:13:38.530 line:80%
Fraud!

00:13:43.860 --> 00:13:44.930 line:80%
Was this from Father?

00:13:47.930 --> 00:13:49.020 line:80%
I'll distract them.

00:13:49.700 --> 00:13:50.886 line:80%
You take the chance to leave.

00:13:51.980 --> 00:13:55.020 line:80%
We are actually both Changs.

00:13:56.690 --> 00:13:57.530 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:13:59.650 --> 00:14:01.530 line:80%
His mother is Mrs. Chang;

00:14:02.140 --> 00:14:03.140 line:80%
my mother

00:14:03.570 --> 00:14:04.690 line:80%
was just a village girl

00:14:04.690 --> 00:14:06.210 line:80%
who had a brief affair with Mr. Chang.

00:14:06.950 --> 00:14:07.980 line:80%
Because of my lowly birth,

00:14:08.449 --> 00:14:10.286 line:80%
I was treated
as Steward Jiang's adopted son,

00:14:10.620 --> 00:14:11.460 line:80%
so I felt resentful.

00:14:12.140 --> 00:14:14.810 line:80%
That day at the grave, I met Lord Song

00:14:15.220 --> 00:14:17.020 line:80%
and learning of the Changs' tragedy.

00:14:17.020 --> 00:14:18.410 line:80%
Then I decided to take his place.

00:14:19.530 --> 00:14:21.650 line:80%
You didn't say that before.

00:14:21.860 --> 00:14:23.140 line:80%
You said

00:14:23.140 --> 00:14:24.410 line:80%
you'd avenge your father.

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:25.500 line:80%
That's true.

00:14:25.860 --> 00:14:27.410 line:80%
Though Mr. Chang disowned me,

00:14:27.780 --> 00:14:28.780 line:80%
he was still my father.

00:14:29.220 --> 00:14:30.140 line:80%
He was killed,

00:14:30.410 --> 00:14:31.330 line:80%
and I must avenge him.

00:14:31.650 --> 00:14:32.490 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:14:33.380 --> 00:14:34.290 line:80%
Both of you

00:14:34.570 --> 00:14:36.620 line:80%
are still suspicious.

00:14:37.330 --> 00:14:38.170 line:80%
Qi,

00:14:38.810 --> 00:14:39.930 line:80%
Xiaofeng and I found

00:14:39.930 --> 00:14:40.780 line:80%
the Changs' belongings

00:14:41.163 --> 00:14:42.629 line:80%
at a pawnshop near Hanhai Mountains.

00:14:42.930 --> 00:14:43.770 line:80%
Following the clues,

00:14:43.933 --> 00:14:45.106 line:80%
we infiltrated the demon sect

00:14:45.500 --> 00:14:47.500 line:80%
and discovered the culprit
is the Demonic Camp.

00:14:48.050 --> 00:14:49.923 line:80%
We learned that over a year ago,

00:14:49.934 --> 00:14:51.507 line:80%
the demon sect had an internal conflict,

00:14:52.330 --> 00:14:54.290 line:80%
the young master Mu Qingyan was killed,

00:14:54.290 --> 00:14:55.140 line:80%
and Nie Zhe

00:14:55.140 --> 00:14:56.380 line:80%
secured the leader position.

00:14:57.620 --> 00:14:59.500 line:80%
Lately, they've expanded their followers

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:00.553 line:80%
and trained death squads,

00:15:00.690 --> 00:15:02.410 line:80%
likely targeting
the Six Sects of Beichen,

00:15:03.506 --> 00:15:04.666 line:80%
planning large-scale revenge.

00:15:08.290 --> 00:15:09.130 line:80%
Alright.

00:15:09.410 --> 00:15:10.650 line:80%
Now, the truth is clear.

00:15:12.220 --> 00:15:13.060 line:80%
For safety,

00:15:13.570 --> 00:15:14.530 line:80%
both of you

00:15:14.930 --> 00:15:16.050 line:80%
should stay here.

00:15:16.530 --> 00:15:17.650 line:80%
As for revenge,

00:15:18.170 --> 00:15:19.380 line:80%
after the memorial,

00:15:19.740 --> 00:15:20.580 line:80%
the Six Sects

00:15:20.810 --> 00:15:22.140 line:80%
will give you an answer.

00:15:28.220 --> 00:15:29.060 line:80%
Thank you, Lord Qi.

00:15:32.220 --> 00:15:33.140 line:80%
Since you can't leave,

00:15:33.900 --> 00:15:35.620 line:80%
Mr. Jiang, why not stay

00:15:36.170 --> 00:15:37.290 line:80%
and help with my herb fields,

00:15:37.690 --> 00:15:39.740 line:80%
as a way to strengthen your health?

00:15:54.290 --> 00:15:55.170 line:80%
You've left.

00:15:56.290 --> 00:15:57.570 line:80%
Why get involved?

00:15:58.150 --> 00:15:59.400 line:80%
I didn't know Father's plan

00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:01.100 line:80%
and almost endangered you.

00:16:03.170 --> 00:16:04.010 line:80%
Sorry.

00:16:09.100 --> 00:16:10.050 line:80%
Your survival

00:16:10.530 --> 00:16:12.780 line:80%
is the greatest comfort

00:16:14.100 --> 00:16:15.100 line:80%
to Mr. Chang's spirit.

00:16:20.690 --> 00:16:21.530 line:80%
Is the culprit

00:16:22.290 --> 00:16:23.930 line:80%
really the Demonic Camp?

00:16:25.180 --> 00:16:26.410 line:80%
Not only them.

00:16:28.620 --> 00:16:30.290 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng is also involved.

00:16:30.860 --> 00:16:32.220 line:80%
Taichu Temple...

00:16:34.100 --> 00:16:35.570 line:80%
I'll avenge the Changs.

00:16:37.500 --> 00:16:38.340 line:80%
Don't act recklessly.

00:16:38.860 --> 00:16:39.810 line:80%
Neither should you.

00:16:51.780 --> 00:16:53.380 line:80%
As the lord of a temple,

00:16:53.810 --> 00:16:55.930 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng ranks in the top ten
among the elites.

00:16:56.620 --> 00:16:57.900 line:80%
Targeting him is suicide.

00:16:58.443 --> 00:16:59.816 line:80%
Master will investigate thoroughly.

00:17:00.020 --> 00:17:01.100 line:80%
You and Mr. Jiang

00:17:01.220 --> 00:17:03.170 line:80%
should just stay here.

00:17:03.780 --> 00:17:04.620 line:80%
Zhao, don't worry.

00:17:04.980 --> 00:17:05.993 line:80%
The Peng bird is injured;

00:17:06.290 --> 00:17:07.130 line:80%
I can't leave either.

00:17:07.477 --> 00:17:09.010 line:80%
The Golden Peng recognizes its master.

00:17:09.460 --> 00:17:10.740 line:80%
How could it obey you?

00:17:13.780 --> 00:17:15.610 line:80%
My father raised it.

00:17:17.370 --> 00:17:18.850 line:80%
I heard from Mother

00:17:19.780 --> 00:17:21.326 line:80%
that Uncle Chang had a harsh childhood

00:17:21.940 --> 00:17:23.130 line:80%
with scarce food.

00:17:24.090 --> 00:17:25.530 line:80%
How could he have raised a Peng bird?

00:17:27.850 --> 00:17:28.690 line:80%
Zhao.

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.220 line:80%
Why don't you ask

00:17:41.570 --> 00:17:42.410 line:80%
who I really am?

00:17:43.756 --> 00:17:45.729 line:80%
Jiang Ning fabricated an identity
to protect you.

00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:48.500 line:80%
Uncle Chang taught you his martial arts

00:17:48.660 --> 00:17:49.610 line:80%
without reservation,

00:17:50.370 --> 00:17:52.220 line:80%
even risking his life to protect you.

00:17:52.700 --> 00:17:53.960 line:80%
I'm sure they had their reasons.

00:17:55.220 --> 00:17:56.810 line:80%
You must be someone they trust.

00:17:59.020 --> 00:17:59.860 line:80%
They trust you;

00:18:00.780 --> 00:18:01.620 line:80%
I trust them.

00:18:02.810 --> 00:18:04.610 line:80%
I don't know your real name yet,

00:18:05.940 --> 00:18:07.330 line:80%
so I'll treat you as Chang Ning.

00:18:07.940 --> 00:18:09.500 line:80%
As long as you do nothing evil,

00:18:10.090 --> 00:18:11.130 line:80%
I'll protect you

00:18:11.700 --> 00:18:13.220 line:80%
and keep you out of danger.

00:18:22.696 --> 00:18:24.020 line:80%
Zhao, you don't need to follow me.

00:18:24.020 --> 00:18:25.176 line:80%
I'm just going to Herb Hut,

00:18:25.420 --> 00:18:26.580 line:80%
not to confront Qiu Yuanfeng

00:18:26.710 --> 00:18:27.670 line:80%
or the demon sect.

00:18:31.050 --> 00:18:32.180 line:80%
This involves the demon sect.

00:18:32.460 --> 00:18:34.050 line:80%
The Six Sects will surely unite,

00:18:34.130 --> 00:18:34.970 line:80%
cooperating fully.

00:18:35.180 --> 00:18:36.130 line:80%
Perhaps by now,

00:18:36.177 --> 00:18:37.616 line:80%
they're already making arrangements,

00:18:37.660 --> 00:18:38.610 line:80%
carrying out their duty.

00:18:47.220 --> 00:18:48.090 line:80%
Truly,

00:18:48.780 --> 00:18:49.940 line:80%
working together

00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:51.660 line:80%
against a common enemy.

00:18:54.940 --> 00:18:56.700 line:80%
How affectionate.

00:18:57.420 --> 00:18:59.050 line:80%
So, it's Zhao

00:18:59.290 --> 00:19:00.700 line:80%
and Chang.

00:19:01.980 --> 00:19:03.980 line:80%
The young master of Peiqiong Manor

00:19:03.980 --> 00:19:05.740 line:80%
is about to arrive.

00:19:05.940 --> 00:19:06.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:07.370 --> 00:19:09.420 line:80%
don't forget your betrothal,

00:19:09.660 --> 00:19:10.940 line:80%
to avoid gossip.

00:19:17.780 --> 00:19:19.090 line:80%
You didn't know?

00:19:19.610 --> 00:19:21.500 line:80%
Zhao is engaged.

00:19:21.780 --> 00:19:24.290 line:80%
Their families are old friends.

00:19:24.660 --> 00:19:26.890 line:80%
The young master, Zhou Yuqi,

00:19:26.890 --> 00:19:27.780 line:80%
and Zhao

00:19:27.850 --> 00:19:29.610 line:80%
are childhood sweethearts,

00:19:29.610 --> 00:19:31.020 line:80%
a perfect match.

00:19:31.290 --> 00:19:32.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:32.220 --> 00:19:33.940 line:80%
why didn't you tell Chang

00:19:34.130 --> 00:19:35.500 line:80%
so he

00:19:35.500 --> 00:19:36.980 line:80%
wouldn't stay

00:19:37.130 --> 00:19:38.220 line:80%
with another man's fiancée?

00:19:40.370 --> 00:19:41.850 line:80%
Do you hear me?

00:19:43.370 --> 00:19:44.740 line:80%
I was looking for Yuzhi.

00:19:44.780 --> 00:19:47.290 line:80%
His fiancée stays with another man.

00:19:47.420 --> 00:19:48.260 line:80%
Yuzhi

00:19:48.330 --> 00:19:49.610 line:80%
is so broad-minded.

00:19:50.050 --> 00:19:50.890 line:80%
You...

00:19:51.050 --> 00:19:51.890 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:52.090 --> 00:19:52.930 line:80%
that's nonsense.

00:19:52.930 --> 00:19:54.300 line:80%
Exactly, nonsense!

00:19:58.850 --> 00:20:00.050 line:80%
Yuqi

00:20:00.460 --> 00:20:02.090 line:80%
is Zhao's fiancé.

00:20:02.980 --> 00:20:04.420 line:80%
When her training ends,

00:20:04.890 --> 00:20:06.930 line:80%
she'll become the young mistress
of Peiqiong Manor.

00:20:09.090 --> 00:20:10.020 line:80%
I heard

00:20:10.570 --> 00:20:12.850 line:80%
Lord Zhou and your aunt
were once engaged,

00:20:13.530 --> 00:20:15.290 line:80%
but he married someone else.

00:20:16.020 --> 00:20:17.940 line:80%
Won't your families have resentment?

00:20:18.370 --> 00:20:19.850 line:80%
What resentment?

00:20:20.290 --> 00:20:22.700 line:80%
My aunt arranged that marriage.

00:20:22.980 --> 00:20:24.090 line:80%
Then why did your aunt

00:20:24.370 --> 00:20:25.810 line:80%
accept this marriage?

00:20:30.330 --> 00:20:31.170 line:80%
Take the medicine.

00:20:36.370 --> 00:20:37.660 line:80%
What kind of person

00:20:38.460 --> 00:20:39.300 line:80%
is Zhou Yuqi?

00:20:41.370 --> 00:20:42.330 line:80%
A refined gentleman,

00:20:42.940 --> 00:20:43.810 line:80%
kind and warm,

00:20:44.500 --> 00:20:45.420 line:80%
nice and friendly,

00:20:45.962 --> 00:20:47.081 line:80%
pleasant as a spring breeze.

00:20:55.050 --> 00:20:56.130 line:80%
Chang,

00:20:56.370 --> 00:20:57.530 line:80%
my Smiley!

00:21:08.460 --> 00:21:09.890 line:80%
Run, run, run!

00:21:11.570 --> 00:21:12.410 line:80%
Don't come over!

00:21:15.180 --> 00:21:16.050 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:18.820 --> 00:21:22.220 line:80%
(Zhou Yuqi, Min Xinrou, Peiqiong Manor)

00:21:25.130 --> 00:21:26.090 line:80%
Yuqi.

00:21:26.290 --> 00:21:27.130 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:21:27.570 --> 00:21:28.410 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:21:29.090 --> 00:21:29.930 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:21:30.530 --> 00:21:32.130 line:80%
I collected many rare items

00:21:32.810 --> 00:21:34.530 line:80%
and came early

00:21:34.810 --> 00:21:35.650 line:80%
with Father

00:21:36.500 --> 00:21:37.700 line:80%
to give them to you.

00:21:40.980 --> 00:21:41.820 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:21:42.530 --> 00:21:44.180 line:80%
where's the big kite you promised me?

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:45.780 line:80%
Xinrou has made it for you.

00:21:45.810 --> 00:21:46.650 line:80%
It's there.

00:21:47.700 --> 00:21:48.930 line:80%
Han, come with me.

00:21:54.980 --> 00:21:55.820 line:80%
Do you like it?

00:22:04.050 --> 00:22:04.890 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:22:05.700 --> 00:22:07.260 line:80%
this is Chang Ning.

00:22:07.660 --> 00:22:08.500 line:80%
Ning,

00:22:10.610 --> 00:22:12.220 line:80%
I was deeply saddened to hear

00:22:12.220 --> 00:22:13.060 line:80%
about the massacre.

00:22:13.570 --> 00:22:14.410 line:80%
Ning,

00:22:14.421 --> 00:22:15.560 line:80%
please accept my condolences.

00:22:15.610 --> 00:22:16.610 line:80%
My father has passed,

00:22:17.736 --> 00:22:19.042 line:80%
and injustice remains unresolved.

00:22:19.190 --> 00:22:20.190 line:80%
No need

00:22:20.330 --> 00:22:21.170 line:80%
for empty sympathy.

00:22:25.810 --> 00:22:27.476 line:80%
My father and Mr. Chang
were old friends.

00:22:27.740 --> 00:22:28.640 line:80%
I especially brought

00:22:28.940 --> 00:22:30.610 line:80%
a Warm Jade Qilin,

00:22:30.621 --> 00:22:32.209 line:80%
conducive to cultivating internal power.

00:22:32.220 --> 00:22:33.220 line:80%
Perfect for Ning.

00:22:49.460 --> 00:22:51.660 line:80%
Then I'll thank you on his behalf.

00:22:51.780 --> 00:22:52.620 line:80%
No need.

00:22:59.220 --> 00:23:00.060 line:80%
What's this?

00:23:00.810 --> 00:23:02.090 line:80%
Xinrou made this hairpin

00:23:02.290 --> 00:23:03.676 line:80%
with mermaid tears for your mother.

00:23:03.700 --> 00:23:04.810 line:80%
I heard she already had one,

00:23:05.290 --> 00:23:06.130 line:80%
so this makes a pair.

00:23:06.870 --> 00:23:08.180 line:80%
You're so thoughtful.

00:23:09.220 --> 00:23:10.060 line:80%
And this?

00:23:10.610 --> 00:23:12.500 line:80%
These are rare storybooks
collected by Xinrou.

00:23:13.020 --> 00:23:14.073 line:80%
Many are unique copies.

00:23:15.330 --> 00:23:16.660 line:80%
I was worried about that.

00:23:17.330 --> 00:23:18.520 line:80%
Xinrou, thank you.

00:23:18.890 --> 00:23:19.730 line:80%
We're family.

00:23:19.940 --> 00:23:20.780 line:80%
No need for thanks.

00:23:33.980 --> 00:23:34.820 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:23:35.130 --> 00:23:36.610 line:80%
why throw a tantrum?

00:23:37.020 --> 00:23:38.446 line:80%
Are you going to listen to your aunt

00:23:38.610 --> 00:23:39.740 line:80%
and marry Zhou Yuqi?

00:23:40.290 --> 00:23:41.196 line:80%
What's wrong with that?

00:23:41.290 --> 00:23:42.510 line:80%
What if he's not right for you?

00:23:42.810 --> 00:23:44.370 line:80%
I can remarry.

00:23:44.940 --> 00:23:45.780 line:80%
Not a big deal.

00:23:46.220 --> 00:23:47.570 line:80%
Marriage is serious.

00:23:48.660 --> 00:23:50.130 line:80%
Your aunt is gone.

00:23:50.530 --> 00:23:51.500 line:80%
If you don't like it,

00:23:52.420 --> 00:23:53.533 line:80%
you can break the betrothal.

00:23:55.130 --> 00:23:56.700 line:80%
Marrying Yuqi is quite good.

00:23:57.460 --> 00:23:58.850 line:80%
Peiqiong Manor is beautiful,

00:23:58.850 --> 00:23:59.810 line:80%
the town is bustling,

00:24:00.460 --> 00:24:02.180 line:80%
and the surrounding cities and towns

00:24:02.180 --> 00:24:03.020 line:80%
have everything.

00:24:03.220 --> 00:24:04.530 line:80%
It's livelier than Luoying Valley.

00:24:05.570 --> 00:24:07.330 line:80%
Yuqi has treated me well
since childhood.

00:24:08.780 --> 00:24:09.940 line:80%
After marriage,

00:24:10.740 --> 00:24:13.020 line:80%
Peiqiong Manor will be mine.

00:24:19.530 --> 00:24:21.530 line:80%
Chang Ning, what are you scheming?

00:24:21.943 --> 00:24:23.669 line:80%
(Determination and Force)
Look at yourself.

00:24:24.020 --> 00:24:25.130 line:80%
Think it about it.

00:24:25.316 --> 00:24:26.700 line:80%
Marriage is not for you to decide.

00:24:26.700 --> 00:24:27.540 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:30.220 line:80%
I'm too young to get married.

00:24:30.660 --> 00:24:32.050 line:80%
Moreover, Grandfather is ill...

00:24:32.370 --> 00:24:34.090 line:80%
He is cared for by the Huangsha gang.

00:24:34.330 --> 00:24:35.180 line:80%
You need not worry.

00:24:35.313 --> 00:24:36.980 line:80%
(Yang Heying)
Marrying into Guangtian Sect

00:24:36.980 --> 00:24:38.882 line:80%
(Sha, Lady of Siqi Sect)
is a rare opportunity.

00:24:38.893 --> 00:24:40.660 line:80%
Why are you so ungrateful?

00:24:40.660 --> 00:24:41.500 line:80%
I...

00:24:41.500 --> 00:24:42.610 line:80%
You are my daughter.

00:24:42.810 --> 00:24:43.940 line:80%
You must obey me.

00:24:44.780 --> 00:24:46.370 line:80%
This is settled; no more discussion.

00:24:48.290 --> 00:24:50.050 line:80%
This is Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

00:25:20.810 --> 00:25:21.700 line:80%
What does he

00:25:22.500 --> 00:25:23.780 line:80%
want again?

00:26:27.530 --> 00:26:28.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:26:29.980 --> 00:26:31.500 line:80%
Did you just see an old woman?

00:26:31.740 --> 00:26:32.780 line:80%
What old woman?

00:26:33.460 --> 00:26:34.530 line:80%
You must've been mistaken.

00:26:34.940 --> 00:26:36.130 line:80%
In the dead of night,

00:26:37.130 --> 00:26:38.420 line:80%
what are you doing here?

00:26:39.260 --> 00:26:40.460 line:80%
(Breeze)

00:26:41.500 --> 00:26:42.340 line:80%
Breeze.

00:26:42.700 --> 00:26:43.940 line:80%
Zhao, do you want to try it?

00:26:44.940 --> 00:26:46.040 line:80%
Your wounds aren't healed.

00:26:46.780 --> 00:26:47.700 line:80%
How can you drink?

00:26:54.100 --> 00:26:55.460 line:80%
(Breeze)

00:26:55.460 --> 00:26:56.780 line:80%
(Why is one jar missing?)

00:27:01.060 --> 00:27:04.500 line:80%
(Breeze)

00:27:13.420 --> 00:27:14.260 line:80%
Father,

00:27:14.420 --> 00:27:15.260 line:80%
Mother,

00:27:15.500 --> 00:27:16.530 line:80%
do you think someone

00:27:16.530 --> 00:27:17.570 line:80%
would steal wine here?

00:27:17.810 --> 00:27:18.980 line:80%
Steal wine?

00:27:20.330 --> 00:27:21.220 line:80%
Of course.

00:27:21.610 --> 00:27:22.810 line:80%
Your aunt has stolen before.

00:27:23.420 --> 00:27:24.610 line:80%
My aunt had such a habit?

00:27:24.660 --> 00:27:25.500 line:80%
Yes.

00:27:26.130 --> 00:27:26.980 line:80%
Your aunt

00:27:27.530 --> 00:27:29.050 line:80%
loved the wine brewed by Lei.

00:27:29.610 --> 00:27:30.450 line:80%
But the ingredients

00:27:31.020 --> 00:27:32.290 line:80%
were rare,

00:27:32.700 --> 00:27:34.220 line:80%
and Lei was reluctant to give more.

00:27:35.290 --> 00:27:36.940 line:80%
So, she went to the wine cellar

00:27:37.290 --> 00:27:38.780 line:80%
with Wu and Yuanrong to steal some.

00:27:38.980 --> 00:27:39.820 line:80%
Is the wine

00:27:39.980 --> 00:27:41.020 line:80%
Breeze?

00:27:41.910 --> 00:27:42.750 line:80%
Come on.

00:27:42.780 --> 00:27:43.780 line:80%
Let's drink.

00:27:43.790 --> 00:27:44.650 line:80%
- Come on.
- Cheers!

00:27:44.660 --> 00:27:45.780 line:80%
- Cheers!
- Come on.

00:27:45.890 --> 00:27:46.730 line:80%
Cheers!

00:27:46.810 --> 00:27:48.330 line:80%
Breeze!

00:27:49.380 --> 00:27:51.640 line:80%
♪In the martial world♪

00:27:51.820 --> 00:27:54.160 line:80%
♪With a shining cup♪

00:27:54.380 --> 00:27:56.310 line:80%
♪I drink with delight tonight♪

00:27:56.890 --> 00:27:58.170 line:80%
♪Free to wander♪

00:27:58.170 --> 00:28:00.580 line:80%
♪In the world♪

00:28:00.580 --> 00:28:01.940 line:80%
(Luo Yuanrong, Taichu Temple)

00:28:02.020 --> 00:28:05.980 line:80%
(Wu Yuanying, Taichu Temple)

00:28:07.890 --> 00:28:09.130 line:80%
Come on.

00:28:09.130 --> 00:28:09.970 line:80%
Here.

00:28:11.370 --> 00:28:12.290 line:80%
Yes, it's Breeze.

00:28:13.500 --> 00:28:14.530 line:80%
That's history.

00:28:15.940 --> 00:28:16.780 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:28:17.290 --> 00:28:18.610 line:80%
those who drank with us then

00:28:19.890 --> 00:28:20.890 line:80%
are all gone,

00:28:21.780 --> 00:28:22.810 line:80%
even Yuanrong

00:28:24.420 --> 00:28:25.570 line:80%
has disappeared.

00:28:33.980 --> 00:28:37.100 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Founder Beichen)

00:29:12.740 --> 00:29:13.580 line:80%
Great-aunt.

00:29:13.580 --> 00:29:15.393 line:80%
(Abbess Jingyuan,
Abbess of Xuankong Nunnery)

00:29:17.460 --> 00:29:18.300 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan.

00:29:24.386 --> 00:29:25.559 line:80%
(Zhou Zhizhen, Peiqiong Manor)

00:29:25.570 --> 00:29:26.410 line:80%
Uncle Zhou.

00:29:42.780 --> 00:29:44.300 line:80%
Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

00:29:44.940 --> 00:29:45.780 line:80%
Strike the bell.

00:30:06.050 --> 00:30:06.890 line:80%
Zhao,

00:30:07.090 --> 00:30:08.290 line:80%
why strike the bronze bell

00:30:08.850 --> 00:30:10.290 line:80%
before the memorial?

00:30:15.250 --> 00:30:16.090 line:80%
This is impressive.

00:30:16.090 --> 00:30:16.930 line:80%
Indeed.

00:30:16.940 --> 00:30:17.840 line:80%
Impressive.

00:30:18.050 --> 00:30:18.890 line:80%
Yes.

00:30:22.290 --> 00:30:23.596 line:80%
The bell was left by the Founder,

00:30:23.980 --> 00:30:25.020 line:80%
cast from underwater iron.

00:30:25.330 --> 00:30:26.520 line:80%
Ordinary people can't ring it.

00:30:26.531 --> 00:30:27.513 line:80%
As expected of Lord Yang.

00:30:27.524 --> 00:30:28.440 line:80%
Officially, it informs

00:30:28.530 --> 00:30:30.020 line:80%
the gods from all directions.

00:30:30.700 --> 00:30:32.530 line:80%
In fact, it intimidates
the martial world:

00:30:33.180 --> 00:30:34.180 line:80%
Without this skill,

00:30:34.290 --> 00:30:36.290 line:80%
don't envy the status of the Six Sects.

00:30:38.340 --> 00:30:39.180 line:80%
Lord Song

00:30:39.180 --> 00:30:40.020 line:80%
of Guangtian Sect.

00:30:40.370 --> 00:30:41.210 line:80%
Strike the bell.

00:31:00.370 --> 00:31:01.610 line:80%
Lord Song is impressive.

00:31:01.850 --> 00:31:03.700 line:80%
His internal force penetrates the bell.

00:31:08.810 --> 00:31:10.050 line:80%
Truly amazing.

00:31:15.370 --> 00:31:16.220 line:80%
Lord Qiu

00:31:16.220 --> 00:31:17.060 line:80%
of Taichu Temple.

00:31:17.500 --> 00:31:18.340 line:80%
Strike the bell.

00:31:57.290 --> 00:31:58.530 line:80%
12 moves from one palm.

00:31:59.890 --> 00:32:00.730 line:80%
12 moves.

00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:04.330 line:80%
There's always

00:32:04.620 --> 00:32:05.460 line:80%
someone better.

00:32:05.460 --> 00:32:06.660 line:80%
As expected of Lord Qiu.

00:32:07.130 --> 00:32:08.740 line:80%
Lord Qiu is peerless.

00:32:09.090 --> 00:32:10.850 line:80%
Not inferior
to the late Ms. Cai Pingshu.

00:32:10.890 --> 00:32:11.740 line:80%
Indeed.

00:32:11.740 --> 00:32:12.890 line:80%
We are enlightened.

00:32:13.780 --> 00:32:14.620 line:80%
You flatter me.

00:32:15.610 --> 00:32:16.450 line:80%
I dare not

00:32:16.740 --> 00:32:19.130 line:80%
compare myself to Ms. Cai.

00:32:19.940 --> 00:32:22.330 line:80%
But I never slack,

00:32:22.810 --> 00:32:23.780 line:80%
practicing day and night,

00:32:25.020 --> 00:32:27.500 line:80%
only to uphold our reputation

00:32:28.420 --> 00:32:30.570 line:80%
and restore our prestige.

00:32:31.290 --> 00:32:32.780 line:80%
Lord Qiu is so upright.

00:32:33.500 --> 00:32:34.252 line:80%
Indeed.

00:32:34.263 --> 00:32:35.220 line:80%
As expected of Lord Qiu.

00:32:35.220 --> 00:32:36.070 line:80%
How upright.

00:32:36.130 --> 00:32:36.970 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:36.970 --> 00:32:38.090 line:80%
Why does he speak like that?

00:32:38.660 --> 00:32:39.500 line:80%
Isn't he saying

00:32:39.740 --> 00:32:41.466 line:80%
that Qingque Sect
has shamed the Six Sects?

00:32:57.149 --> 00:32:58.569 line:80%
The auspicious time of the memorial

00:32:58.780 --> 00:32:59.620 line:80%
can't be delayed.

00:33:19.660 --> 00:33:20.500 line:80%
They vanished.

00:33:25.370 --> 00:33:26.290 line:80%
This is incredible.

00:33:28.940 --> 00:33:30.420 line:80%
Qingque Sect is still the best.

00:33:30.660 --> 00:33:31.760 line:80%
No wonder it's the top sect.

00:33:31.953 --> 00:33:32.943 line:80%
Worthy of its reputation.

00:33:33.700 --> 00:33:34.780 line:80%
Lord Qi is impressive.

00:33:40.940 --> 00:33:42.980 line:80%
Your Beichen Way

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:44.530 line:80%
softens hardness.

00:33:44.886 --> 00:33:46.326 line:80%
The greatest sound is almost silent.

00:33:46.610 --> 00:33:47.700 line:80%
It has reached perfection.

00:33:48.130 --> 00:33:49.370 line:80%
I respect it.

00:33:51.370 --> 00:33:52.530 line:80%
Thank you for your praise.

00:33:55.330 --> 00:33:56.170 line:80%
Everyone,

00:33:57.130 --> 00:33:58.290 line:80%
in times of peace,

00:33:58.700 --> 00:33:59.700 line:80%
with the world at ease,

00:34:00.530 --> 00:34:03.610 line:80%
we honor the Founder

00:34:04.180 --> 00:34:07.930 line:80%
and pay tribute to the spirit
of Founder Beichen.

00:34:08.580 --> 00:34:10.660 line:80%
We hope all martial peers

00:34:11.290 --> 00:34:13.620 line:80%
will join our Six Sects,

00:34:14.290 --> 00:34:16.060 line:80%
uphold justice for the people,

00:34:16.620 --> 00:34:18.810 line:80%
take the safety of the common folk
as our duty,

00:34:19.540 --> 00:34:20.760 line:80%
and promote the righteous path.

00:34:21.290 --> 00:34:22.810 line:80%
Promote the righteous path.

00:34:23.580 --> 00:34:25.010 line:80%
Promote the righteous path.

00:34:30.890 --> 00:34:32.976 line:80%
You're the one
who broke into the cellar last night.

00:34:33.580 --> 00:34:34.490 line:80%
Who exactly are you?

00:34:37.890 --> 00:34:39.383 line:80%
You are Cai Pingshu's niece, right?

00:34:40.780 --> 00:34:42.930 line:80%
Why are you helping
these cold-blooded beasts?

00:34:44.930 --> 00:34:45.890 line:80%
You know my aunt?

00:35:13.970 --> 00:35:15.010 line:80%
Who are you?

00:35:15.700 --> 00:35:17.490 line:80%
Why barge in here

00:35:17.580 --> 00:35:18.700 line:80%
and ruin our memorial?

00:35:24.330 --> 00:35:25.170 line:80%
Ms. Luo?

00:35:26.740 --> 00:35:27.580 line:80%
Yuanrong.

00:35:30.370 --> 00:35:31.210 line:80%
Yuanrong.

00:35:32.620 --> 00:35:33.460 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:35:34.010 --> 00:35:35.620 line:80%
I'm the disciple of Master Canghuan,

00:35:35.660 --> 00:35:37.010 line:80%
former lord of Taichu Temple.

00:35:37.780 --> 00:35:38.700 line:80%
Why shouldn't I come?

00:35:41.140 --> 00:35:41.980 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:35:42.340 --> 00:35:43.210 line:80%
I came here because...

00:35:43.220 --> 00:35:44.060 line:80%
Yuanrong,

00:35:52.560 --> 00:35:54.786 line:80%
this is the 200th anniversary
of the Founder's passing.

00:35:55.370 --> 00:35:57.140 line:80%
Such a solemn and serious day.

00:35:57.850 --> 00:35:59.010 line:80%
If you act rashly,

00:36:00.780 --> 00:36:02.740 line:80%
I'll have to kill you.

00:36:03.060 --> 00:36:03.900 line:80%
Yuanfeng,

00:36:05.490 --> 00:36:06.726 line:80%
Yuanrong may be stubborn,

00:36:06.737 --> 00:36:08.026 line:80%
but she doesn't deserve to die.

00:36:08.100 --> 00:36:08.940 line:80%
Silence.

00:36:12.740 --> 00:36:13.580 line:80%
Yuanrong,

00:36:14.660 --> 00:36:16.140 line:80%
for the sake of our shared fellowship,

00:36:17.010 --> 00:36:18.580 line:80%
return with me to Taichu Temple.

00:36:19.850 --> 00:36:20.810 line:80%
I won't harm you.

00:36:21.620 --> 00:36:22.460 line:80%
Senior Qiu,

00:36:23.010 --> 00:36:24.330 line:80%
Ms. Luo has managed to come here.

00:36:24.740 --> 00:36:26.026 line:80%
Surely, she has an urgent matter.

00:36:26.850 --> 00:36:28.010 line:80%
Why do you keep stopping her?

00:36:28.660 --> 00:36:30.100 line:80%
This is within our sect.

00:36:30.660 --> 00:36:32.450 line:80%
How can a junior speak now?

00:36:33.100 --> 00:36:34.740 line:80%
Yuanrong was our childhood friend.

00:36:35.410 --> 00:36:36.620 line:80%
She lost her beloved.

00:36:37.180 --> 00:36:38.620 line:80%
It's not easy that she survived.

00:36:39.100 --> 00:36:40.060 line:80%
She's here today;

00:36:40.580 --> 00:36:42.010 line:80%
why not let her speak?

00:36:43.700 --> 00:36:44.580 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan,

00:36:46.060 --> 00:36:46.900 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:36:47.580 --> 00:36:50.010 line:80%
I do not intend to cause trouble
on the memorial,

00:36:52.370 --> 00:36:54.330 line:80%
but without everyone present,

00:36:55.780 --> 00:36:58.060 line:80%
I fear my immense grievance
can't be voiced.

00:36:59.290 --> 00:37:01.540 line:80%
Please, for my late master's sake,

00:37:03.010 --> 00:37:04.490 line:80%
allow me to speak a few words.

00:37:04.740 --> 00:37:05.580 line:80%
Luo Yuanrong,

00:37:07.026 --> 00:37:08.666 line:80%
you've caused enough trouble
these years.

00:37:08.930 --> 00:37:10.780 line:80%
Why not retreat now?

00:37:11.060 --> 00:37:11.900 line:80%
Lord Qiu,

00:37:13.700 --> 00:37:14.660 line:80%
it's reached this point.

00:37:15.060 --> 00:37:16.290 line:80%
Rather than suppress it,

00:37:16.660 --> 00:37:18.660 line:80%
it's better to reveal everything

00:37:19.290 --> 00:37:20.620 line:80%
and clear the misunderstanding

00:37:20.930 --> 00:37:22.370 line:80%
before the Founder's spirit.

00:37:24.290 --> 00:37:25.740 line:80%
It truly is a misunderstanding.

00:37:27.740 --> 00:37:29.180 line:80%
As you all know,

00:37:29.810 --> 00:37:31.540 line:80%
Wu Yuanying of our sect

00:37:32.330 --> 00:37:34.580 line:80%
died over ten years ago
in a battle with the demon sect.

00:37:36.060 --> 00:37:37.290 line:80%
However,

00:37:37.890 --> 00:37:40.370 line:80%
since then,

00:37:40.930 --> 00:37:43.220 line:80%
Yuanrong could not let go,

00:37:43.540 --> 00:37:44.850 line:80%
insisting he was still alive.

00:37:46.060 --> 00:37:48.180 line:80%
For over ten years,
she's repeatedly pressured us

00:37:48.890 --> 00:37:50.700 line:80%
to infiltrate the demon sect
to rescue him,

00:37:50.700 --> 00:37:51.930 line:80%
or falsely claimed

00:37:51.930 --> 00:37:53.330 line:80%
I killed Yuanying,

00:37:55.780 --> 00:37:57.330 line:80%
wrongly accusing me.

00:37:57.810 --> 00:37:58.650 line:80%
At that time,

00:37:59.290 --> 00:38:00.810 line:80%
Master learned that the demon sect used

00:38:00.810 --> 00:38:02.356 line:80%
living humans to create corpse slaves.

00:38:04.010 --> 00:38:05.450 line:80%
He resolved to protect the people.

00:38:06.970 --> 00:38:08.290 line:80%
He called martial heroes,

00:38:09.100 --> 00:38:10.060 line:80%
split into groups,

00:38:10.413 --> 00:38:12.313 line:80%
and went to the Hanhai Mountains
to fight evil.

00:38:13.580 --> 00:38:14.420 line:80%
That day,

00:38:16.370 --> 00:38:18.290 line:80%
everyone battled the demon sect.

00:38:19.740 --> 00:38:21.180 line:80%
Yuanying and his team

00:38:22.180 --> 00:38:25.010 line:80%
encountered Elder Kaiyang
of Nie Hengcheng.

00:38:26.010 --> 00:38:27.450 line:80%
Knowing he could not win,

00:38:28.270 --> 00:38:29.700 line:80%
- he shouted for retreat.
- Retreat!

00:38:29.780 --> 00:38:30.810 line:80%
(Young Qiu Yuanfeng)

00:38:30.810 --> 00:38:33.330 line:80%
But Qiu Yuanfeng, greedy for merit,

00:38:34.740 --> 00:38:36.330 line:80%
recklessly attacked.

00:38:38.290 --> 00:38:39.660 line:80%
Kaiyang was infuriated.

00:38:40.780 --> 00:38:42.010 line:80%
Yuanying, disregarding danger,

00:38:42.010 --> 00:38:43.236 line:80%
sacrificed himself to save him.

00:38:45.620 --> 00:38:46.540 line:80%
- Run!
- Okay!

00:38:47.410 --> 00:38:49.810 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng abandoned Yuanying

00:38:50.060 --> 00:38:51.140 line:80%
and fled.

00:39:05.780 --> 00:39:06.620 line:80%
Exactly.

00:39:07.370 --> 00:39:08.810 line:80%
That day, Yuanying saved me.

00:39:10.180 --> 00:39:12.330 line:80%
But I'm not cowardly.

00:39:13.490 --> 00:39:15.150 line:80%
I only escaped

00:39:15.490 --> 00:39:16.330 line:80%
by Yuanying's orders.

00:39:16.703 --> 00:39:18.060 line:80%
When Yuanying told you to escape,

00:39:18.060 --> 00:39:19.220 line:80%
you didn't.

00:39:19.430 --> 00:39:20.290 line:80%
You caused trouble,

00:39:20.290 --> 00:39:21.890 line:80%
provoked Kaiyang, and ran away?

00:39:22.180 --> 00:39:23.020 line:80%
Lord Qiu,

00:39:23.450 --> 00:39:25.370 line:80%
take responsibility
for the mess you caused.

00:39:26.290 --> 00:39:27.450 line:80%
Running after causing havoc?

00:39:27.780 --> 00:39:29.010 line:80%
Isn't that

00:39:29.010 --> 00:39:30.010 line:80%
leaving Yuanying to die?

00:39:33.620 --> 00:39:34.700 line:80%
I'll never forget

00:39:35.450 --> 00:39:36.620 line:80%
the life-saving debt.

00:39:37.620 --> 00:39:38.460 line:80%
But ultimately,

00:39:39.370 --> 00:39:41.060 line:80%
we were all trying to defeat the demon.

00:39:42.370 --> 00:39:43.370 line:80%
How am I wrong?

00:39:44.180 --> 00:39:45.290 line:80%
Yuanying isn't dead!

00:39:45.290 --> 00:39:47.220 line:80%
Your obsession

00:39:47.220 --> 00:39:48.780 line:80%
has disrupted the sect.

00:39:49.220 --> 00:39:50.780 line:80%
Yuanying is dead!

00:39:50.850 --> 00:39:52.450 line:80%
Yuanying is alive.

00:39:59.970 --> 00:40:02.140 line:80%
You are so stubborn.

00:40:05.660 --> 00:40:06.500 line:80%
Fine.

00:40:07.290 --> 00:40:08.700 line:80%
If what you say is true,

00:40:09.970 --> 00:40:12.060 line:80%
produce convincing evidence.

00:40:29.140 --> 00:40:32.700 line:80%
(Wu Xiong, Wu Gang, Taichu Temple)

00:41:30.780 --> 00:41:31.620 line:80%
Yuanying,

00:41:36.180 --> 00:41:37.020 line:80%
I'm Qi Yunke.

00:41:37.620 --> 00:41:38.460 line:80%
Can you hear me?

00:41:44.410 --> 00:41:45.250 line:80%
Yuanying!

00:41:48.490 --> 00:41:49.330 line:80%
Yuanying!

00:41:55.220 --> 00:41:56.780 line:80%
These demon sect beasts

00:41:56.780 --> 00:41:58.450 line:80%
are worse than animals.

00:42:10.140 --> 00:42:11.180 line:80%
Impossible.

00:42:13.140 --> 00:42:14.370 line:80%
I saw him die

00:42:19.370 --> 00:42:20.540 line:80%
with my own eyes.

00:42:25.450 --> 00:42:26.700 line:80%
Where did you find him?

00:42:28.410 --> 00:42:30.096 line:80%
You must've colluded
with the demon sect.

00:42:30.660 --> 00:42:31.500 line:80%
You are right.

00:42:32.850 --> 00:42:34.180 line:80%
I indeed entered the demon sect.

00:42:35.060 --> 00:42:36.220 line:80%
Over a year ago,

00:42:36.810 --> 00:42:38.780 line:80%
I once again clashed with Qiu Yuanfeng.

00:42:40.290 --> 00:42:41.450 line:80%
Why didn't you save Yuanying?

00:42:41.740 --> 00:42:42.580 line:80%
Let go!

00:42:42.620 --> 00:42:43.460 line:80%
Tell me!

00:42:48.660 --> 00:42:49.620 line:80%
Expel her.

00:42:50.220 --> 00:42:51.060 line:80%
Yes.

00:42:52.010 --> 00:42:53.410 line:80%
He severely injured me.

00:42:54.890 --> 00:42:56.490 line:80%
Mr. Chang Haosheng saved me.

00:43:08.850 --> 00:43:09.690 line:80%
Yuanrong?

00:44:12.140 --> 00:44:16.060 line:80%
(Chang Fort)

00:44:27.060 --> 00:44:33.100 line:80%
(Chang Fort)

00:45:47.890 --> 00:45:50.290 line:80%
I disguised myself
as an ugly scavenger woman

00:45:51.890 --> 00:45:53.410 line:80%
and searched every dungeon and prison

00:45:53.410 --> 00:45:55.370 line:80%
along Youming Path

00:45:57.330 --> 00:45:58.810 line:80%
for a whole year.

00:46:00.796 --> 00:46:02.100 line:80%
Finally, in the EightClaw Prison,

00:46:02.100 --> 00:46:03.700 line:80%
I found Yuanying.

00:46:19.140 --> 00:46:19.980 line:80%
Yuanying!

00:46:23.010 --> 00:46:25.410 line:80%
His eyes were gouged, his tongue cut,
and ligaments severed.

00:46:26.100 --> 00:46:27.100 line:80%
He was soaked in poison.

00:46:31.620 --> 00:46:32.890 line:80%
For over ten years,

00:46:35.290 --> 00:46:36.370 line:80%
Yuanying lived

00:46:36.370 --> 00:46:37.970 line:80%
a life worse than death,

00:46:39.540 --> 00:46:40.380 line:80%
tormented little

00:46:40.660 --> 00:46:41.500 line:80%
by little

00:46:42.370 --> 00:46:43.970 line:80%
to this state.

00:46:45.540 --> 00:46:46.410 line:80%
You knew all along?

00:46:49.290 --> 00:46:50.930 line:80%
I did not know Yuanying was alive.

00:46:52.700 --> 00:46:53.540 line:80%
Even if I did,

00:46:54.930 --> 00:46:56.930 line:80%
returning would've been certain death.

00:47:00.220 --> 00:47:01.740 line:80%
What could I do?

00:47:02.410 --> 00:47:03.410 line:80%
Many

00:47:03.780 --> 00:47:05.290 line:80%
survived the great battle.

00:47:07.330 --> 00:47:08.970 line:80%
I tracked them down one by one,

00:47:09.850 --> 00:47:11.060 line:80%
asked carefully

00:47:11.060 --> 00:47:11.970 line:80%
and clearly.

00:47:13.660 --> 00:47:14.580 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng,

00:47:15.450 --> 00:47:17.410 line:80%
could you really not save Yuanying?

00:47:17.970 --> 00:47:19.740 line:80%
You harbored resentment for him,

00:47:21.140 --> 00:47:22.580 line:80%
thinking that as long as he lived,

00:47:23.370 --> 00:47:24.930 line:80%
you'd have no chance to rise.

00:47:24.970 --> 00:47:26.620 line:80%
So, you abandoned him.

00:47:27.230 --> 00:47:29.340 line:80%
Everyone, don't let her fool you.

00:47:30.100 --> 00:47:31.490 line:80%
Yuanying has been trapped

00:47:31.490 --> 00:47:33.620 line:80%
in the demon sect's prison for years.

00:47:34.180 --> 00:47:35.930 line:80%
How could he be rescued easily

00:47:36.140 --> 00:47:38.450 line:80%
and happen to appear at the memorial?

00:47:39.140 --> 00:47:40.450 line:80%
This is the demon sect's plot

00:47:41.600 --> 00:47:42.450 line:80%
to slander me,

00:47:42.450 --> 00:47:43.370 line:80%
sow discord,

00:47:43.370 --> 00:47:44.370 line:80%
and divide our Six Sects.

00:47:44.890 --> 00:47:46.850 line:80%
How evil their hearts are.

00:47:46.850 --> 00:47:47.690 line:80%
Qiu Yuanfeng,

00:47:48.290 --> 00:47:50.060 line:80%
do you still want to twist the truth?

00:47:51.290 --> 00:47:52.620 line:80%
I only want to prevent Yuanying

